com.tsgrp.migration.event

Class PrecedenceParerListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.tsgrp.migration.event.AbstractListener
      • com.tsgrp.migration.event.PrecedenceParerListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    SourceEndExportNodeEventListener

    public class PrecedenceParerListener
extends AbstractListener
implements SourceEndExportNodeEventListener
    Problem- too many folder links Solution- PrecendenceParser This listener will take in a list of possible fodler paths, ranked by priority from top to bottom. they are compared to all paths stored in om_folder and will set om_folder to be the single folder of highest priority found. NOTE: This listener does not support the AbstractListener's processVersionsForListeners injectable and will not work correctly if it is configured when instantiating this listener.
    Since:
    Feb 4, 2011
